{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Selection.removeRange()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/removeRange","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/anchorNode\"><code>anchorNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/anchorOffset\"><code>anchorOffset</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/focusNode\"><code>focusNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/focusOffset\"><code>focusOffset</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/isCollapsed\"><code>isCollapsed</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/rangeCount\"><code>rangeCount</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/addRange\"><code>addRange()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/collapse\"><code>collapse()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/collapseToEnd\"><code>collapseToEnd()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/collapseToStart\"><code>collapseToStart()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/containsNode\"><code>containsNode()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/deleteFromDocument\"><code>deleteFromDocument()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/extend\"><code>extend()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/getRangeAt\"><code>getRangeAt()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/modify\"><code>modify()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/removeAllRanges\"><code>removeAllRanges()</code></a></li><li><em><code>removeRange()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/selectAllChildren\"><code>selectAllChildren()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/setBaseAndExtent\"><code>setBaseAndExtent()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection/toString\"><code>toString()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概述","isH3":true,"content":"<p>将一个区域从选区中移除。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"用法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><i>sel</i>.removeRange(<i>range</i>)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect1\">\n  <i>\n   <code>range</code></i>\n </dt>\n <dd>\n  Range 对象将从选区当中移除。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">/* 通过设计一段 js 代码，我们可以获得多个区域，\n * 这段代码可以移除除了第一个区域之外的所有区域。\n *（此代码在 Chrome 中不生效，因为 Chrome 当中只能\n * 选择一个选区，哎我为什么要在 Mozilla 的网站上\n * 说这个？译者注）*/\n\ns = window.getSelection();\nif(s.rangeCount &gt; 1) {\n for(var i = 1; i &lt; s.rangeCount; i++) {\n  s.removeRange(s.getRangeAt(i));\n }\n}\n</pre>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"将一个区域从选区中移除。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Selection.removeRange()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"removeRange","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"removeRange","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/selection/removerange","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/selection/removerange/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/